attributes.name: RSO | Syringe
attributes.body: What is RSO? Put simply, RSO is an oil derived from cannabis. But rather than a solvent extract that strips trichomes from buds, RSO contains all the cannabinoids, terpenes, and additional compounds of the whole cannabis plant. The extraction process is complex and fairly long, similar to making a tincture. It’s typically near-black in color, and, admittedly, doesn’t taste great due to its high amount of plant matter (it uses the whole plant). RSO was created as a medicinal therapeutic for cancer and other chronic health conditions, like MS and asthma. While Rick Simpson no longer produces the oil himself, it remains a crucial ingredient in the treatment plans of patients across North America.

When many companies cut corners, using inferior ingredients like animal-derived gelatin and artificial sweeteners, we crafted a vegan, terpene-enhanced, melt-proof recipe that virtually any adult could enjoy. While our competitors waited for state regulations to require testing, we tested our products for potency and consistency from the start. And now, more than a decade later, customers all over the U.S. and Canada trust us to deliver a premium cannabis experience, every time they reach for a Wana product.

attributes.name: Forbidden Cake | Outdoor
attributes.body: Cross between Wedding Cake x Forbidden Fruit In 2015 we were shovel ready and applied but were denied licensure due to political shenanigans in Santa Fe. Unwilling to accept defeat or wait years to start this journey we are grateful that one badass company known as Urban Wellness with great forward thinking leaders gave us a chance to prove our concepts and build a track record of success working under their license. That lasted from 2016 though 2021 when we were awarded the first production license following the passage of the Cannabis Regulation Act. Getting our own license allowed us to scale our systems and grow our community. Today we work with 15 groups of contractors/people that make up the #LavaLeafCollective or #FarmFamily working on our property. We have also helped 4 family owned companies with similar values to obtain licensure and to get their cultivation operations off the ground. One major differentiator that we hope becomes the norm, is that we do not hire growers we partner with them. We believe that business owners will take more pride in and responsibility for their work. This means that more love and care is given to each nugget of flower Lava Leaf produces. New Mexico is home to many great producers so high quality is now par for the course. Now we are leveling up our systems and driving a conversation around equity and the sustainability of cannabis production. When purchasing cannabis we hope people will question, how was this grown? Was it a sustainable use of water and power? Does this company recycle? Are the growers or creators of this product valued?

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Concord Cream
attributes.body: Concord Cream, a predominantly Indica strain, is the sweet sweet love child of Grape Bubba and Cookies & Cream. This soothing bud, rich in flavor, is a must-try for any grape strain fans. True to its name, Concord Cream boasts a super sweet and creamy fruity grape flavor complemented by notes of flowery violet and vanilla. The aroma mirrors this profile with a hint of sour grapefruit. Concord Cream is a favored choice for addressing various conditions across a whole spectrum, including stress, anxiety, muscle spasms, cramps, depression, and insomnia. The Concord Cream high unfolds gradually, initiating with a slow burn of euphoria that melts the mad/sad away. Concord Cream is wonderful for consumers that have social anxiety as its a very talkative, giggly strain! As the mental boost persists, a sense of physical relaxation takes over, eventually inducing a sleepy, sedative state.

attributes.name: Golden Poppy
attributes.body: Prohibition 37 flower is our specialty and what we have built our brand on. Our production facilities include 2 state-of-the-art indoor cultivations totaling 14,000 sq ft in our home city of Albuquerque. We also have an outdoor farm in Belen, and greenhouse productions in Belen and Gallup. Our mission is to destigmatize the industry, produce outstanding quality cannabis, and positively contribute to the quality of life of our patients and customers. We currently grow over 75 cultivars, and are continually adding the newest and most sought after genetics to bring to every corner of New Mexico. WHO IS P37? Prohibition 37 is a physician-led, nationally recognized, and award-winning vertical cannabis company. P37 is highly focused on the customer experience and science of the medicinal and recreational effects of its many products. Our name is derived from The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937, which was a U.S. federal law that effectively criminalized the possession and distribution of marijuana. While it did not directly ban the cannabis plant, it imposed strict regulations and heavy taxes on its cultivation, sales, and use. This made it impossible to legally engage in these activities, leading to a de facto prohibition of cannabis. The Act played a significant role in shaping the modern approach to marijuana regulation in the United States.\ SOCIAL EQUITY AND JUSTICE The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937 disproportionately targeted minorities, particularly African, Mexican, and Jewish American communities. While the act did not explicitly mention racial or ethnic groups, its implementation and enforcement were marked by tremendous racial bias and discrimination. Law enforcement, for example, selectively targeted and arrested individuals from minority groups and used marijuana-related offenses as a pretext for discriminatory actions. This contributed to the disproportionate impact of the Act on minorities, perpetuating racial stereotypes and injustices for generations to come. Our mission at Prohibition 37 is to reverse decades of cannabis-related injustice and create a healthy, communal, and scientific approach to cannabis use.

attributes.body: King Louis XIII (Indica) : Our variety of King Louis XIII has a royally strong and pleasant scent primarily consisting of pine with some earthy tones mixed in. Effects include relaxed, sleepy, and happy. Orale! ORALE vape carts and disposables are distilled 3 times to create a refined distillate that is void of all impurities and has maximum THC potency levels to elevate your enchantment and pure satisfaction. attributes.name: Rhianna | Phuse Blunt
attributes.body: Pharmers Quality Concentrates is New Mexico’s premier manufacture of high-end concentrates. We are the chemistry focused cannabis extraction laboratory in Socorro, New Mexico. We strive to provide the highest quality cannabis oil available by imploring the use of modern organic chemistry. We specialize in cannabinoid extraction, distillation, isolation, and remediation of contaminants. We believe it is important to trust the source of your medicine. Along time ago before marijuana prohibition, people were able to purchase Cannabis Oil at Pharmacies across the country. These pharmacies sold classily, trusted brands of medicine made by chemists with a true want to help and provide relief to their consumers. These brands were proud and stood by their medicine and so do we. Our motto is QUALITY COMES STANDARD because we believe it should! Our highly qualified staff of Laboratory Technicians will ensure that the utmost care is taken in the handling, extraction, and processing of your Cannabis oils. Selection of quality biomass is key to obtaining the best tasting and greater yielding concentrates. Let us work with your company to provide your patients with the best medication in New Mexico.

attributes.name: Frenchy Pebbles | Disposable
attributes.body: Live Extraction As opposed to drying and curing, the essence of the living cannabis plant is preserved through freezing immediately after harvest and remaining frozen throughout extraction. This process retains a broader spectrum of live terpenes and cannabinoids in higher volumes, yielding an exotic alternative to traditional BHO extracts. Live BHO typically resembles that of the plant in its final stage of flowering when terpene potency is at its peak generating robust aromatics and delivering unmatched piquancy. Adding enticing nuances to the typical cannabis extract palate, live extracts have become the first choice of the modern connoisseur. Traditional Extraction Utilizing dried and cured cannabis, this process extracts the cannabinoids, along with the aroma and flavor of the plant you love into a powerful concentrate. The best extracts of cannabis leave behind many of the carcinogenic substances the plants produce while preserving the desirable contents they contain. Cannabis extract can manifest a variety of dynamic textures, consistencies, and useful by-products such as H.T.S.F.E. Furthermore, cannabis extract has become the industry’s preferred method for infusing activated cannabinoids, such as ?9-THC, into ingestible and topical products. Refined Extraction Take into consideration the environmental pollutants and agricultural contaminants that can be associated with cannabis cultivation, the subsequent extracts can contain unwanted impurities, pigments, and even harmful chemicals. Our proprietary filtration techniques and chromatography methodologies allow us to remediate compromised or otherwise undesirable extracts while maintaining the desirable components such as cannabinoids and terpenes. The end result meets all standards for consumption from shelf-ready solid extract to liquid and food-grade variations. By making these processes available, we aim to help eliminate large-scale waste associated with the ever-expanding industry of commercial cannabis.

attributes.name: Blueberry | Classic Gummies
attributes.body: Infused with a terpene-enhanced indica blend, these not-too-sweet, not-too-tart gummies evoke feelings of relaxation and calm. What Makes Us Wana? Excellence. We've never been satisfied with "good enough," not even when we were just a scrappy Boulder-based start-up trying to make our way in a newly legalized industry. When many companies cut corners, using inferior ingredients like animal-derived gelatin and artificial sweeteners, we crafted a vegan, terpene-enhanced, melt-proof recipe that virtually any adult could enjoy. While our competitors waited for state regulations to require testing, we tested our products for potency and consistency from the start. And now, more than a decade later, customers all over the U.S. and Canada trust us to deliver a premium cannabis experience, every time they reach for a Wana product.
